{"tid":971137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶男子以微信支付擷圖假裝已付款 詐騙麵店食足半年霸王餐","createTime":"2019-01-06T11:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T11:56:48.000Z","uid":51464,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"623f7b5e33b5ac14888672e49064e3c465482f3c","tid":971137,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2243772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2243772&d=keks8wIK6uKY2hr1SzdLk3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=ddd2c8e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2243772</a><br />\n使用手機 QR Code 作為支付方式的支付寶（Alipay）和微信支付（ＷeChat Pay），在大陸已非常流行。近年香港也開始推廣使用 QR Code 手機支付模式，除了綠色專線小巴會率先支援 AlipayHK 易乘碼外，港鐵預計亦會在 2020 年推出支援 QR Code 手機支付方式的閘機。不過，QR Code 手機支付在安全性，始終存在隱憂。大陸重慶有 1 名男子，便利用靜態 QR Code 手機支付的安全漏洞進行詐騙，在麵店食足半年霸王餐！<br />\n==========<br />\n大陸只有騙子是真！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}